&lt;p&gt;A 37.5 hour permanent post has become available within Blaenau Gwent Locality for a staff nurse who wishes to develop their career within community nursing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role includes a 12 month opportunity within Tredegar District Nursing Team followed by a post either within District Nursing or at Ysbyty Aneurin Bevan Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited from motivated and enthusiastic individuals with a flexible approach who are committed to providing high standards of care to people within their own home and local community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date: 8th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
